quote_first: I didn't sleep too long, because I think it was only
quote_last: when I woke up. I felt pretty hungry as soon as I had a cigarette. The last time I'd eaten was those two hamburgers I had with Brossard and Ackley when we went in to Agerstown to the movies. That was a long time ago. It seemed like fifty years ago.
title: Catcher in the Rye
author: J.D. Salinger
